<LocalizedProperties><Language>en</Language><Title>Security Update for Exchange 2000 Server (KB906780)</Title><Description>A security issue has been identified that could affect your Exchange 2000 Server system in the following way: 1. Denial of Service 2. Elevation of Privilege 3.Tampering with Data 4. Information Disclosure . We recommend that you install this update on all Microsoft Exchange 2000 servers in your organization.</Description><UninstallNotes>Uninstall is available from "Add or Remove Programs" in the Control Panel.</UninstallNotes><MoreInfoUrl>http://support.microsoft.com/?kbid=906780</MoreInfoUrl><SupportUrl>http://www.microsoft.com/technet/treeview/default.asp?url=/technet/prodtechnol/exchange/</SupportUrl></LocalizedProperties>